      <title>派拉蒙的 Redstone 将获得 1.8 亿美元的遣散费和福利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/paramount-s-redstone-to-reap-180-million-in-severance-benefits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，派拉蒙全球董事长莎莉·雷石东 (Shari Redstone) 将获得 1.8 亿美元的遣散费和其他福利，此外还将获得将其股票出售给电影制片人大卫·埃里森 (David Ellison) 领导的财团所得的数亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/paramount-s-redstone-to-reap-180-million-in-severance-benefits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:51:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
