      <title>亿万富翁 Sicupira 在重组后离开 Americanas 董事会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/billionaire-sicupira-leaves-americanas-board-after-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西亿万富翁卡洛斯·西库皮拉 (Carlos Sicupira) 将离开 Americanas SA 董事会，此前一场 250 亿雷亚尔（45 亿美元）的会计欺诈案震惊了这家零售商，并将其推入破产保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/billionaire-sicupira-leaves-americanas-board-after-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
